import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router, Event as RouterEvent, NavigationEnd } from '@angular/router'; import { filter } from 'rxjs/operators'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = 'final-swe642-project'; showHeaderFooter = true; // Controls the visibility of the header and footer constructor(private router: Router) { // Listen to route changes this.router.events.pipe( filter((event: RouterEvent): event is NavigationEnd => event instanceof NavigationEnd) ).subscribe((event: NavigationEnd) => { // Hide the header and footer for "Survey Form" and "List All Surveys" pages this.showHeaderFooter = !(event.urlAfterRedirects === '/survey-form' || event.urlAfterRedirects === '/list-surveys'); }); } } Welcome Page
  • Survey Form
  • List All Surveys

Welcome to the Final Project of SWE642
